# Control summary
# One line summary of script for inclusion in the
# package 'control' file.
# This, in turn, is displayed by many package managers.
# Must be no longer than 60 characters.
# Required. One only.
control-summary find directories needing album cover art

# Control description
# Description of script. This is a longer description
# than the one line summary and can stretch over
# multiple lines. Each line can be no longer than
# 60 characters. Paragraphs can be separated by a line
# consisting of a single period ('.'). This description
# will be included in the package 'control' file. This,
# in turn, is displayed by many package managers.
# Required. Multiple allowed.
control-description Search the current directory recursively for subdirectories
control-description that need album cover art. More specifically, it searches
control-description for subdirectories containing mp3 files but no album cover
control-description art file. An album cover art file is one named F<album.png>,
control-description F<album.jpg>, F<cover.png>, or F<cover.png>.
control-description .
control-description The subdirectories matching these conditions are printed to
control-description STDOUT, one per line.

